main event: Four bright amber lights were observed moving over Springfield, Missouri for about 3 minutes.
interesting points: The lights were traveling west to east, with one light disappearing as the other two got closer.
The lights faded to the east after about 3 minutes of observation.
The witness, a 19-year-old unemployed female, seemed to be a reliable observer.
The local radio station and police had received multiple phone calls about UFO sightings in the area around the same time.
No evaluation could be made with the information available at the time.
sighted object: four bright amber lights in the sky
